name: Two thumbs up for the Cool Wall with Tammer Saleh, founder of SuperOrbital (Ship It! #65)
summary: Tammer Saleh, founder of Super Orbital, a tiny team of exceptional Kubernetes engineers and teachers, is joining us today to talk about what is cool in the Cloud Native world.
